---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Jaden Raats"
  description="Learn about my journey into development and what drives me to build."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="main-content">
          <!-- TODO(human): Customize this section with your personal story -->
          <h2>My Story</h2>
          <p>
            I'm a self-taught developer who believes in learning by building. While I don't have a traditional
            computer science degree, I've developed my skills through hands-on projects, online resources, and
            a commitment to continuous learning.
          </p>

          <p>
            What started as curiosity about how websites work has grown into a passion for creating solutions
            that solve real problems. I approach each project as an opportunity to learn something new and
            improve my craft.
          </p>

          <h2>What Drives Me</h2>
          <p>
            I'm motivated by the challenge of turning complex problems into simple, elegant solutions. I believe
            the best way to learn is by building, failing, iterating, and improving. Every project teaches me
            something new about both technology and problem-solving.
          </p>

          <p>
            I'm currently exploring opportunities where I can contribute to meaningful projects while continuing
            to grow as a developer. I'm particularly interested in roles where I can learn from experienced teams
            and make a tangible impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar">
          <div class="skills-section">
            <h3>Technical Skills</h3>
            <!-- TODO(human): Update with your actual tech stack -->
            <div class="skills-list">
              <span class="skill-badge">JavaScript</span>
              <span class="skill-badge">HTML & CSS</span>
              <span class="skill-badge">React</span>
              <span class="skill-badge">Node.js</span>
              <span class="skill-badge">Git & GitHub</span>
              <span class="skill-badge">Astro</span>
              <span class="skill-badge">Responsive Design</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="learning-section">
            <h3>Currently Learning</h3>
            <!-- TODO(human): Add technologies you're currently studying -->
            <ul class="learning-list">
              <li>TypeScript</li>
              <li>API Development</li>
              <li>Database Design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="approach-section">
            <h3>My Approach</h3>
            <ul class="approach-list">
              <li>üéØ Focus on solving real problems</li>
              <li>üìñ Learn through building</li>
              <li>üîç Attention to detail</li>
              <li>üí¨ Clear communication</li>
              <li>üîÑ Continuous improvement</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .page-header {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0 var(--spacing-md);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .about-content {
      padding: var(--spacing-md) 0 var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .main-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }

    .main-content h2:first-child {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .main-content p {
      color: var(--color-text-light);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .sidebar {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .skills-section,
    .learning-section,
    .approach-section {
      background: var(--color-card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .sidebar h3 {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }

    .skills-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .skill-badge {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .learning-list,
    .approach-list {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .learning-list li,
    .approach-list li {
      padding: 0.25rem 0;
      color: var(--color-text-light);
    }

    .learning-list li::before {
      content: "‚Üí ";
      color: var(--color-primary);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    @media (max-width: 968px) {
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: var(--spacing-md);
      }

      .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
